@lasers can you just change this
```
@author Maxim Baz (https://github.com/maximbaz), @lasers
```

Also can you add it __as a single extra commit__.   That way I'll merge right away.  If you add it in with the existing commit I'll need to review it all again which may not be for several days.

The input can be in the format:
e.g: stype : {'csr', 'default', 'row_sparse'}
In which case we need to get rid of the "{}" and set the type as string. This part is just a part of the data cleaning

maybe something like:

