```

Yeah I saw that but I what I didn't realize was...
>The directory is readable, writable, and searchable only by the creating user ID.

@waprin thanks for pointing it out in your notes and thanks @tseaver for the fix!

>  I'd prefer to use different keys and just put both under transport

That is what I meant, e.g.:

```
config = {
  'transport': {
     'udp': { ... },
     'matrix': { ... },
  }
}
```

Right now the transport configuration is sort of spread out.
